quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  4,24,"Harminanaama on kadi resugol : …ďen rew…ďe jommbaa…ďe ; si wanaa …ďen …ďe jeytir…óon √Īaame mon ka konehoyri fii laawol Alla, hino daganii on renndugol e …ďen …óon tuma …ďe laa…ďiri fiilordu. Alla Farlii …óum e dow moo…óon, O Daginani on ko wanaa …ďen rew…ďe …óon, nde …óa…ď…ďirton la…ď…ďingol pittaali mon kon ko dagii hara wanaa faandagol jinaa. Kala mon dakmitor…óon e ma…ď…ďe desal, jonnee mo teŇče makko …óe Alla Wa…óani…ďe …óen farilla wa…ó…óii…óo on, bakkaatu alanaa on e kon ko yarlondirton …óuytugol maa …ďeyda teŇče wa…ó…óii…óe …óen …ďaawo …óum happeede. Pellet, Alla Laatike Anndu…óo tagu Makko ngun, huunde suu…óaaki Mo e ma…ď…ďe, √Ďee√Īu…óo e Toppitagol Makko ngol e Sar'ia."
  4,25,"Kala e mon onon wor…ďe …ďen mo hattanaaka resugol rew…ďe seŇčii…ďe sabu baasal yaajireede, hino daganoo mo resugol …ďen …ďe o jeytiri √Īaamo makko ngon ; si …ďen laatike gom…óim…ďe. Ko Alla ∆Āuri Anndude haqiiqa gom…óinal mon e ko wirnii e fiyaake mon, onon e …ďen rew…ďe, hi…óon fota ka diina e ka ne…ó…óaaku, wata on towniŇčtinano resugol …ďen. Resiree…ďe duŇčayee maw…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, jonniron …ďe teŇče ma…ď…ďe …óen no haaniri ; si tawii ko …ďe laa…ďu…ďe hara wanaa fe√Ī√Īinoo…ďe jinnduru mun wanaa kadi njaatotoo…ďe fii ko jeenida e ma…ď…ďe. Si …ďe resaama, …ďe faggitike paŇčkare jinaa, focciree…ďe feccere paatawol rin…óum…ďe …ďen : …óum woni paatawol cappan…óe jowi, …ďe rajmetaake, ko rin…óu…ďe …ďen piyetee haa maaya si …ďe jinii ko …ďe resaa…ďe. Kon ko jaŇčtaa …óon e dagagol resude hor…ďe gom…óim…ďe laa…ďu…ďe, ko hoynangol on hulan…óo hoore-mun yanugol e jinaa, fii o maraa feere resugol rin…óu…ďe …ďen, wonnde mu√Ī√Īorgol desal hor…ďe …ďen …ďuri. Alla ko Haforanoowo kala tuubu…óo e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen, Hinnotoo…óo …ďe. No jeyaa e Hinnayee Makko on : Sar'inangol …ďe resugol hor…ďe …ďen tuma tawi feere alaa ko resira rin…óum…ďe …ďe, fii hulugol jeeno."
  4,26,"Alla Senii…óo On ko Faandorii Sar'ingol …óee √Īaawooje, ko ∆Āannginanngol on doose Diina Makko kan, e kon ko mo∆ī∆īinanta on aduna e laakara, Himo Faadori …óum kadi Fewnirgol on laawi Annabaa…ďe …ďen ado mon : ka dagingol harmina e ka jikkuuji ma…ď…ďe tedduu…ói, e fillayeeji ma…ď…ďe yettinii…ói ; fii yo on √Īemtim…ďe. Himo Faandii kadi ruttugol on e geddi adda on e …óoftaare. Alla ko Anndu…óo mo∆ī∆īere jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen, √Ďee√Īu…óo e Sari'aaji Makko e Toppitagol fiyakuuji ma…ď…ďe."